### OpenClaw Migration: Single Agent to Multi-Agent Configuration

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/multi-agent-sandbox-tools.md

Demonstrates the structural change required when migrating from a single-agent OpenClaw configuration to a multi-agent setup. The example shows the transition from a basic `agents.defaults` structure to a more granular `agents.list` with specific agent configurations.

```json
{
  "agents": {
    "defaults": {
      "workspace": "~/.openclaw/workspace",
      "sandbox": {
        "mode": "non-main"
      }
    }
  },
  "tools": {
    "sandbox": {
      "tools": {
        "allow": ["read", "write", "apply_patch", "exec"],
        "deny": []
      }
    }
  }
}
```

```json
{
  "agents": {
    "list": [
      {
        "id": "main",
        "default": true,
        "workspace": "~/.openclaw/workspace",
        "sandbox": { "mode": "off" }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

