### Manage Git Stashes for Multi-Agent Safety

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/AGENTS.md

Guidelines for managing Git stashes in a multi-agent environment. Agents should avoid creating or applying stashes unless explicitly requested to prevent interference with other agents' work.

```git
# Do not create/apply/drop git stash entries unless explicitly requested.
# Avoid git pull --rebase --autostash.
# Assume other agents may be working; keep unrelated WIP untouched.
```

