### Git Worktree and Branch Management for Multi-Agent Safety

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/AGENTS.md

Rules for managing Git worktrees and branches to maintain multi-agent safety. Agents must not create, remove, or modify worktrees, nor switch branches, unless explicitly instructed.

```git
# Do not create/remove/modify `git worktree` checkouts (or edit `.worktrees/*`) unless explicitly requested.
# Do not switch branches / check out a different branch unless explicitly requested.
```

