### Handling Unrecognized Files in Multi-Agent Workflows

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/AGENTS.md

Guidance for agents encountering unrecognized files during their work. The instruction is to ignore such files and focus on committing only the changes relevant to the agent's task.

```git
# When you see unrecognized files, keep going; focus on your changes and commit only those.
```

