### Setup Anthropic Authentication for Models

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/cli/index.md

Configures authentication for Anthropic models using the `setup-token` command. It requires the `openclaw` CLI and optionally accepts a `--yes` flag to bypass confirmation prompts.

```bash
claude setup-token
openclaw models auth setup-token --provider anthropic
openclaw models status
```

