### Multi-platform Channel Setup

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/gateway/configuration-examples.md

Configures communication channels for the agent, including WhatsApp, Telegram, and Discord. It allows specifying phone numbers or user IDs for incoming messages.

```json
{
  "channels": {
    "whatsapp": { "allowFrom": ["+15555550123"] },
    "telegram": {
      "enabled": true,
      "botToken": "YOUR_TOKEN",
      "allowFrom": ["123456789"]
    },
    "discord": {
      "enabled": true,
      "token": "YOUR_TOKEN",
      "dm": { "allowFrom": ["yourname"] }
    }
  }
}
```

