### OpenProse Integration

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/tools/lobster.md

OpenProse can orchestrate multi-agent preparation, followed by a Lobster pipeline for deterministic approvals. Allow the `lobster` tool for sub-agents via `tools.subagents.tools`.

```APIDOC
## OpenProse

OpenProse pairs well with Lobster: use `/prose` to orchestrate multi-agent prep, then run a Lobster pipeline for deterministic approvals. If a Prose program needs Lobster, allow the `lobster` tool for sub-agents via `tools.subagents.tools`. See [OpenProse](/prose).
```

