### Configure Global Coding Profile and Messaging Agent

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/multi-agent-sandbox-tools.md

This JSON configuration applies a default 'coding' tool profile to all agents and then specifically configures the 'support' agent to use a 'messaging' profile, allowing only the 'slack' tool. This demonstrates setting global defaults and overriding them for specific agents.

```json
{
  "tools": { "profile": "coding" },
  "agents": {
    "list": [
      {
        "id": "support",
        "tools": { "profile": "messaging", "allow": ["slack"] }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

