### Non-Interactive Vercel AI Gateway Setup (Bash)

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/providers/vercel-ai-gateway.md

Performs a non-interactive setup for Vercel AI Gateway with OpenClaw in local mode. It requires the AI Gateway API key to be provided as an environment variable.

```bash
openclaw onboard --non-interactive \
  --mode local \
  --auth-choice ai-gateway-api-key \
  --ai-gateway-api-key "$AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY"
```

