### OpenClaw CLI Setup and Channel Login

Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/start/setup.md

Commands to set up OpenClaw and log in to channels. Assumes OpenClaw CLI is installed globally or via pnpm.

```bash
openclaw setup
openclaw channels login
